title: 09/10/21 DPS Hour 3 Joe Torre and Kurt Warner
itunes:title: 09/10/21 DPS Hour 3 Joe Torre and Kurt Warner
description:
Joe Torre talks to Dan about the emotions he felt during 911. Joe tells Dan how it was to continue to play baseball while New York was grieving after the attacks of 911. Kurt Warner tells Dan that Cowboy fans should feel pretty good today.
